<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="45">Distribution and ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="45">The species is known only from the type specimen, collected from Kibale National Park in Uganda, where it was reportedly growing on a leaning, dead branch.</paragraph>
